data.description: Welcome to your spacious 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom haven! This inviting residence offers a perfect combination of comfort and convenience, making it the ideal place to call home. With its large fenced backyard, hardwood floors, wood-burning fireplace, and ample storage, this property has all the elements for a delightful living experience.    The open kitchen and living room layout provides lots of space and storage allowing you to cook your favorite meal while visiting with family or friends.   The family room downstairs features a wood-burning fireplace serves as the heart of the home, offering cozy warmth and a charming focal point for gatherings and relaxation.      With five bedrooms, this home offers ample space for personalization. Whether you need extra rooms for family, guests, or a home office, you'll find the versatility you need.  The primary bedroom has it's own attached bathroom and closet space.    The large fenced backyard is a fantastic feature, providing a private space for outdoor activities, gardening or entertainment. The included shed offers additional storage for your outdoor equipment and tools, keeping your yard organized and tidy.    This home has a convenient cul-de-sac location and is within a close communte to parks, schools, shopping, I-25 and Ft. Carson.  With a little love and personal touch you can make it your own!  Don't miss the opportunity to take a look today!
